# The Origins

Garrett Rodgers was born in Poplar Bluff, Missouri in the year 2000. Shortly into his life he moved to Puxico, Missouri, then finally when he turned ten he moved to Trinity, Alabama. [The Journey](The-Journey.md) after reaching Alabama has been a long one, but the time spent in Missouri prior to this time was still half of his life. He went to the Junior High School in Puxico, Missouri (Please see below) where he met one of his best friends to this day, Jake. Jake eventually went to [Southeast Missouri State University](https://semo.edu/), while Garrett went on to eventually attend the [University Of Missouri](https://missouri.edu/), ultimately reuniting the friends to the same state, but not the same school.
